* Liquid Clustering
** Recommended Approach
***_ New tables (Databricks Runtime 13.3+)
***_ CLUSTER BY (col1, col2, ...) up to 4 keys
** How it Works
***_ Incremental clustering on OPTIMIZE
***_ Schedule OPTIMIZE every 1-2 hours
** Flexibility
***_ Change keys without rewriting
***_ ALTER TABLE ... CLUSTER BY (new_keys)
***_ OPTIMIZE FULL to rewrite all data
** Automation
***_ CLUSTER BY AUTO (predictive optimization)
***_ Auto-selects best keys from query patterns
@endmindmap
